title: Are Celebrity Makeup Brands Just A Cash Grab?
description:
As beauty gurus, we know that makeup is a multi-million dollar industry that can make or break a brand. So when we see a celebrity with no previous makeup experience (we're looking at you, Kanye!), we have to wonder... is it all just a cash grab? In today's episode, the first recorded in our NEW studio, we review makeup brands from the celebrities you all know and love.
